*{{cite book |author=Kissinger, Henry A. |year=1999 |title=Years of Renewal |isbn=0-684-85572-0 |publisher=Touchstone |location=New York}} by Secretary of State
*{{cite book |author=Thompson, Kenneth (ed.) |year=1980 |title=The Ford Presidency: Twenty-Two Intimate Perspectives of Gerald Ford |isbn=0-8191-6960-9 |publisher=University Press of America |location=Lanham}}
{{Refend}}

