*Jespersen, T. Christopher. &quot;The Bitter End and the Lost Chance in Vietnam: Congress, the Ford Administration, and the Battle over Vietnam, 1975–76&quot;. ''Diplomatic History'' 2000 '''24'''(2): 265–293. {{ISSN|0145-2096}} Fulltext: in Swetswise, Ingenta, Ebsco
